{
  "stem": "16571.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they picked-- from there again they picked different people to-- in-- from Buchenwald itself, they were taking people to different parts of the country for work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was picked to go to this [GERMAN], I call it today.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Block 8.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were just a stone's throw from Appellplatz, where people used to have to stand for hours on end to be counted.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In row-- sometimes there was somebody missing, or maybe not and they miscounted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they used to have to stand out all night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we were again lucky because in this blockade, we were let in after the officer, the German officer, came to count us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were let in into the block because we learned in about two or three minutes-- we learned where our spot is.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if they came to-- to count us again, we were virtually there as if we stayed there all the time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So once again, it-- it's only because he was a very nice-- this guy was a Czech kapo.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe he was Czech.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a very nice-- if there was somebody nice, he was nice there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because everybody was after everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody-- there was no friends, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You just numbers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this particular person, he felt that-- that we could go indoors while they were-- somebody was missing or somebody got lost or some-- and we were lucky in that respect.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Food wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was short food, but it wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember we-- we-- they used to have a lot of German Jews in a couple of blocks in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
